{"tid":1826575,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯指若23條立法應繞過內會  稱今日不做還待何時","createTime":"2020-01-16T08:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T02:26:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d56d7fcea978e711d5779274a0de2bc78f5847ed","tid":1826575,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"政府提出將涉及增加產假的僱傭條例修訂，繞過立法會內務委員會及成立法案委員會，改由人力事務委員會審議。建制派議員何君堯同意做法，又指即使政府為《基本法》23條立法，立法會亦應該繞過內會，一併完成首讀、二讀及三讀。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，建制派於立法會擁有43席，但仍然不能盡《基本法》責任，認為屬於愧對選民，指內會被癱瘓，認為任何有需要處理的法案，都應該直接繞過內會處理，即使如果特首提23條立法，首讀、二讀及三讀都要即時處理。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又指，如果特首推動23條立法，他會承擔，亦會全力推動，形容「今日不做，還待何時」，又指他在議會只爭朝夕，如果本屆立法會未能做到，不能期望往後的立法會再為23條立法，認為特首不需要等到2022年特首選舉才為23條立法。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503129-20200116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503129-20200116.htm&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GG8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=dbf746ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503129-20200116.htm&h=3e32f287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503129-20200116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0708405718bee114ef7078e6f87867aa8ba3bace","tid":1826575,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57d97d869408dac221358a125ab2c7f4582b75c2","tid":1826575,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" 